==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Massy
<hw>Mass"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <amorph>[<pos>Compar.</pos>
<adjf>Massier</adjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>superl.</pos>
<adjf>Massiest</adjf>.]</amorph> <def>Compacted into, or consisting of,
a mass; having bulk and weight or substance; ponderous; bulky and heavy;
weighty; heavy; <as>as, a <ex>massy</ex> shield; a <ex>massy</ex>
rock.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Your swords are now too <qex>massy</qex> for your strengths,⟦br⟧
And will not be uplifted.</q> <rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Yawning rocks in <qex>massy</qex> fragments fly.</q>
<rj><qau>Pope.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mast</ent>⟦br⟧
